METAMAGIC

Usage: ^gMETAMAGIC^n

Metamagic is a set of powerful techniques learnt by initiates.
They go above and beyond normal magic lessons but require intense
study and dedication to use. The metamagic command shows you a
list of metamagics you know. Ones in red require you to seek out
a teacher to teach you more about the subject.

^WSee Also: INITIATE, INITIATION, MASKING, CLEANSING, REFLECTION^n
